{"tid":2373180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[做家務嘅入]洗衣機洗完啲衫仲好臭","createTime":"2021-01-20T09:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T12:26:28.000Z","uid":77320,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bdb85a11411d1c7de862b8fc2f8a7d7b63689a10","tid":2373180,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:07:29.000Z","msg":"今朝洗咗第一機衫<br />\n洗完成浸m血味,好撚臭<br />\n初頭以為老母買錯柔順劑<br />\n擺落洗衣機再洗多次<br />\n今次冇落柔順劑<br />\n洗完都係同一陣m血味<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二次洗落咗嘅有洗衣粉(正常,冇臭味),滴露(大量)<br />\n最近屋企有個老人家經常用洗衣機(佢平時唔用,唔知係咪因為天口凍唔想手洗)<br />\n而佢啲衫就好撚臭嘅<br />\n唔知關唔關事，因為同佢啲衫唔係同一機洗<br />\n而家我就嚟窒息"},{"pid":"a40a7ce38c90f872c4dc7d851c0121ff3c14e44f","tid":2373180,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:08:40.000Z","msg":"之前洗衫用同一份量滴露<br />\n完全冇臭味仲香噴噴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a132d7e32253b55836703f32fb904eccd61e8afe","tid":2373180,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:10:19.000Z","msg":"如果係因為屋企老人家啲衫洗完搞到洗衣機臭<br />\n正常到我洗第二次嘅時候都應該冇咗浸味<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cf24d072bd806da8c521f36656339628bfc27b","tid":2373180,"uid":241832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"佢用完冇打開部機等乾先閂？"},{"pid":"9b3b46b8c98c960671f174c16dc2d24c41e69e06","tid":2373180,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:11:18.000Z","msg":"洗機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86550d6a9b12888853236661817dc54240c9a26b","tid":2373180,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b3b46b8c98c960671f174c16dc2d24c41e69e06","tid":2373180,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:11:18.000Z","msg":"洗機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:11:53.000Z","msg":"又係你秒覆我<i